#Challenge 2 :

As per the shared document and research, i believe we can use below command to get the JSON output.
https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/rest/api/compute/virtual-machines/get?tabs=HTTP

HTTP: GET https://management.azure.com/subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.Compute/virtualMachines/{vmName}?api-version=2023-07-01
Optional prameters: GET https://management.azure.com/subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.Compute/virtualMachines/{vmName}?$expand={$expand}&api-version=2023-07-01
